'''Thruncan''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Vodran/Legends|Vodran]].<ref name="LoNH">''[[Lords of Nal Hutta]]''</ref>

The [[Thruncan Insurrection]] took place there when the native [[Vodran (species)/Legends|Vodran]] rebelled against [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] occupation. Prior to the Insurrection, the city had a population in the millions. Afterward, only a few thousand remained.<ref name="LoNH" />

